s:4098:"<p class="mt25">{mlang en} </p><p class="mt25"></p><p>To
be featured and considered as one of Efham Business Experts, you should:</p>

<p>1.    
<span dir="ltr"></span>Sign up
as an expert on Efham Business Website.</p>

<p>2.    
<span dir="ltr"></span>Check <b><u>our
material</u></b> to be ready for taking the Expert’s Exam.</p>

<p><b>3.   
</b><span dir="ltr"></span>Go
through <b><u>Experts Terms and Conditions.</u></b><b><u></u></b></p>

<p>4.    
<span dir="ltr"></span>Go
through <b><u>Criteria of Endorsement</u></b> in your field.</p>

<p>5.    
<span dir="ltr"></span>If an
expert didn’t pass or complete the exam during the first trial, the Expert must
wait for <b>6 months</b> before retaking the exam. At that time, Experts can
check <b><u>our material</u></b> to be ready for the second trial.</p>

<p> </p>

<p><b>I,
